data.description: Large home, on property, with irrigation, in town, close to amenities! This house has it all; two large primary suites, two living areas, a loft, an open floor plan kitchen, dedicated eating area, and loads of charm.  The home is finished with a rustic cabin feeling, featuring wood details and a beautiful river rock fireplace, and is light and bright with windows and skylights to bring in the sun. With ductless units in the bedrooms, two pellet stoves, and a fireplace, you will stay comfortable in all seasons.  Decks off both primaries, as well as the dining area bring outside to your doorstep and provide the perfect quiet hideaway.   Step outside to your 2 acre irrigated yard, with fruit trees, a pasture, and space to play. The current barn is great for storage or add whatever you need for all your hobbies.  This property has space for it all, your RV storage, your hobbies, and your loved ones.  Schedule your private showing of this unusual Bend gem today!
